data.yamlPipeline:
pipeline:
    name: testPipeline_Cypress
    identifier: testPipeline_Cypress
    projectIdentifier: defaultproject
    orgIdentifier: default
    tags: {}
    stages:
        - stage:
              name: jenkinsTrigger
              identifier: jenkinsTrigger
              description: ""
              type: Deployment
              spec:
                  serviceConfig:
                      serviceRef: sa
                      serviceDefinition:
                          spec:
                              variables: []
                              artifacts:
                                  primary:
                                      identifier: ""
                                      spec:
                                          connectorRef: testConnector
                                          artifactPath: sa
                                          build: <+input>
                                          jobName: AutomationQA
                                      type: Jenkins
                          type: ServerlessAwsLambda
                  execution:
                      steps:
                          - step:
                                type: ShellScript
                                name: ss
                                identifier: ss
                                spec:
                                    shell: Bash
                                    onDelegate: true
                                    source:
                                        type: Inline
                                        spec:
                                            script: echo 1
                                    environmentVariables: []
                                    outputVariables: []
                                    executionTarget: {}
                                timeout: 10m
                      rollbackSteps:
                          - step:
                                name: Serverless Lambda Rollback
                                identifier: ServerlessLambdaRollback
                                type: ServerlessAwsLambdaRollback
                                timeout: 10m
                                spec: {}
                  infrastructure:
                      environmentRef: sa
                      infrastructureDefinition:
                          type: ServerlessAwsLambda
                          spec:
                              connectorRef: testConnectorAws
                              stage: testStage
                              region: testRegion
                      allowSimultaneousDeployments: false
              tags: {}
              failureStrategies:
                  - onFailure:
                        errors:
                            - AllErrors
                        action:
                            type: StageRollback
